\begin_layout Section
Special tables
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The dia model contains two special tables Domains and MetaData.
 These are no real tables but contain meta data for the model.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Domains
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This meta table contains the domains that are use in the model.
 All columns of all real tables should use domains for data types.
 These domains are defined in this meta table.
\end_layout

